{"tid":1300443,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【撤回評級】惠譽撤回對長實所有評級 長實：標普、穆迪仍可供投資者參考 (17:00)","createTime":"2019-07-09T11:12:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T12:47:28.000Z","uid":28765,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d1fc4fe9edba82f5a746d057576c3ac4524f1aa3","tid":1300443,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:12:15.000Z","msg":"文章日期：2019年7月9日<br />\n<br />\n惠譽向投資者發布消息表示，由於長實集團(1113)不再向惠譽提供相關資料，故惠譽將撤回對長實集團的長期外幣信貸評級「A」，展望為「穩定」、高級無擔保債券評級「A」及早前由長實地產發行30億美元規模的歐元中期票據的「A」評級。<br />\n<br />\n惠譽表示，由於長實選擇停止參與評估程序，故惠譽無法在不充份的資料下維持該集團的評級，此後惠譽將不再向投資者提供與長實相關的評級資訊。<br />\n<br />\n長實發言人回應本報查詢時承認，集團的確沒有繼續參與惠譽的評估程序，惟仍然有向標普及穆迪這兩間評級機構提供資料，強調集團財政非常穩健，相信金融機構仍有足夠的評級資訊可以參考。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1562664411693&amp;issue=20190709\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1562664411693%26issue%3D20190709&d=xVNj5QJXHW0KkW%2Bw8ZKC7BVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=6b22eef0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1562664411693%26issue%3D20190709&h=f381fb9e\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1562664411693&amp;issue=20190709</a>"},{"pid":"a406a20a9e3a8776e80b85f931ba63e8e2d1bd46","tid":1300443,"uid":91813,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:18:49.000Z","msg":"fitch不嬲垃圾<br />\ns&amp;p同moody&lsquo;s夠晒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57419aab04e81f605ebcbadc16cb1b3ac9d19ece","tid":1300443,"uid":54884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:57:54.000Z","msg":"其實要俾幾多錢呢d 公司"},{"pid":"fe4b1e448824ad5ac740eb026572617b4265147d","tid":1300443,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T12:47:28.000Z","msg":"就係呢啲撚屌公司搞到有次按危機"}]}